remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 Il <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObjectCollection.Add%2A> metodo prevede solo <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> e i tipi derivati (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, e <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) come parametri. Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrata l'aggiunta di uno schema incluso per la <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> raccolta di un oggetto esistente <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> oggetto.  
  
```vb  
Dim schema As XmlSchema = New XmlSchema()  
  
Dim textReader As XmlTextReader = New XmlTextReader("include.xsd")  
Dim includeSchema As XmlSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null)  
  
Dim include As XmlSchemaInclude = New XmlSchemaInclude()  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```  
  
```csharp  
XmlSchema schema = new XmlSchema();  
  
XmlTextReader textReader = new XmlTextReader("include.xsd");  
XmlSchema includeSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null);  
  
XmlSchemaInclude include = new XmlSchemaInclude();  
include.Schema = includeSchema;  
schema.Includes.Add(include);  
```
